metadata.description:
Yearning for the destination and nostalgia for the places left behind are connected by the train station, where people part from each other, and depart from cities. Just like memories of the past and longing for the future are intertwined in the present moment. A girl is sitting in the bar imagining her future, unconsciously bidding farewell to her hometown. Luckily fate is too inscrutable for her to be aware of this fact.  
 
2100x2625, mp4  
Animation and music by Yu Cai
